H0.text: What was the occupation of Lovely Rita according to the song by the Beatles. Parking Attendant

H1.text: What was the occupation of Lovely Rita according to the song by the Beatles. Traffic Warden

H2.text: What was the occupation of Lovely Rita according to the song by the Beatles. Police Officer

H3.text: What was the occupation of Lovely Rita according to the song by the Beatles. Metermaid

A4.text: The term 'meter maid' was popularised in The Beatles' song 'Lovely Rita'.

A5.text: The term 'parking attendant' is sometimes considered a synonym but sometimes used to refer to the different profession of parking lot attendant.
